{"id":1672,"date":"2024-08-23T21:24:39","date_gmt":"2024-08-23T21:24:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1672"},"modified":"2024-08-23T21:24:39","modified_gmt":"2024-08-23T21:24:39","slug":"ampharosite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/","title":{"rendered":"Ampharosite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"big center text-large\">Ampharosite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Gift from the white-haired mega trainer on Thundercap Mountain 2F after defeating him. Requires Rock Climb to reach.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Ampharos<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Antisis City<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm08-rock-climb\/\">Rock Climb<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Defeat every trainer on Thundercap Mt.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Head west from the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/01-pokemon-unbound-going-west-from-the-antisis-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Going west from the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going west from the Antisis City Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Walk down the stairs and continue going west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/02-pokemon-unbound-continuing-west-after-walking-down-the-stairs.jpg\" alt=\"Continuing west after walking down the stairs. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Continuing west after walking down the stairs.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter Thundercap Mt. from the east entrance.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/03-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-mountain.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the mountain \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the mountain<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After entering the mountain, jump off the ledge to the north and follow the path up.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/04-pokemon-unbound-jumping-off-the-ledge-to-the-north.jpg\" alt=\"Jumping off the ledge to the north. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Jumping off the ledge to the north.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Climb the stairs to your west to get on the rocky platform then instantly get off using the stairs to the south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/05-pokemon-unbound-climbing-up-the-platform-and-getting-off-it-using-the-south-stairs.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing up the platform and getting off it using the south stairs. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing up the platform and getting off it using the south stairs.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue going south by jumping off a ledge and following the path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/06-pokemon-unbound-jumping-down-the-south-ledge-and-following-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Jumping down the south ledge and following the path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Jumping down the south ledge and following the path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually see a white-haired NPC you can reach using Rock Climb. Speak with him after defeating the rest of the trainers on the mountain and he\u2019ll challenge you to a battle.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/07-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-mega-trainer.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Mega Trainer. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Mega Trainer.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Defeating this elite trainer will give you the Ampharosite.<\/p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table grey left\" style=\"min-width:860px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"6\" class=\"text-large\">Mega Trainer Aloysius<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/08-pokemon-unbound-mega-trainer-aloysius.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/09-pokemon-unbound-politoad.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/10-pokemon-unbound-blissey.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/11-pokemon-unbound-braviary.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/12-pokemon-unbound-reuniclus.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/ampharosite\/13-pokemon-unbound-mega-ampharos.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Pok\u00e9mon<\/th>\n<td>Politoad (Level 58 at Tessy level cap)<\/td>\n<td>Blissey (Level 57 at Tessy level cap)<\/td>\n<td>Braviary (Level 61 at Tessy level cap)<\/td>\n<td>Reuniclus (Level 58 at Tessy level cap)<\/td>\n<td>Mega Ampharos (Level 59 at Tessy level cap)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Water<\/td>\n<td>Normal<\/td>\n<td>Normal\/Flying<\/td>\n<td>Psychic<\/td>\n<td>Electric\/Dragon<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ability<\/th>\n<td>Drizzle<\/td>\n<td>Natural Cure<\/td>\n<td>Sheer Force<\/td>\n<td>Regenerator<\/td>\n<td>Tangling Wool \u2013 Mold Breaker<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Held Item<\/th>\n<td>Damp Rock<\/td>\n<td>Chople Berry<\/td>\n<td>Wacan Berry<\/td>\n<td>Colbur Berry<\/td>\n<td>Ampharosite<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weaknesses<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Grass (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Electric (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Rock (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Electric (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Ice (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Ghost (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Dark (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Ground (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Ice (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Dragon (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Moves<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Scald<\/li>\n<li>Ice Beam<\/li>\n<li>Perish Song<\/li>\n<li>Hypnosis<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Mud Bomb<\/li>\n<li>Toxic<\/li>\n<li>Minimize<\/li>\n<li>Soft-Boiled<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Brave Bird<\/li>\n<li>Crush Claw<\/li>\n<li>Superpower<\/li>\n<li>U-Turn<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Psychic<\/li>\n<li>Thunder<\/li>\n<li>Shadow Ball<\/li>\n<li>Trick Room<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Thunder<\/li>\n<li>Dragon Pulse<\/li>\n<li>Power Gem<\/li>\n<li>Thunder Wave<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__